{"tid":1155313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這樣也違法？為愛犬取名「城管」 支那男子被關10天","createTime":"2019-05-15T00:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T23:54:45.000Z","uid":32511,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0303682d24a435f7b50e82f2406bd97979245acb","tid":1155313,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:54:15.000Z","msg":"連取名的自由也沒有？中國安徽省一名男子把愛犬取名為「城管」、「協管」，竟因此涉嫌違法，背上「尋釁滋事」罪名，被行政拘留10日。<br />\n <br />\n根據中國媒體報導，安徽省阜陽市一名班姓男子多次在通訊軟體群組發布消息，稱把狗取名為「城管」、「協管」。阜陽市公安局潁州分局沙河路派出所13日接獲報警後，傳喚班男到派出所接受調查。<br />\n <br />\n年近30的班男主要收入來源是養狗賣狗，他供稱，給狗取這樣的名字只是因為覺得好玩，「我不懂法，不知道這是違法的」，並對自己的行為非常後悔。班男最後因「尋釁滋事」，被處行政拘留10日。<br />\n <br />\n對此，有不少中國網友表示不知道此舉違法，有人更嘲諷「尋釁滋事是個好東西」、「到底誰在尋釁滋事」，「這樣定罪，手是不是伸得太長了」。<br />\n <br />\n還有不少網友更直言，取這2個名字是在侮辱狗，「作為一個有良知的人，我奉勸你一句，你不能用這2個詞侮辱狗狗」。"},{"pid":"f13b0f311f9234f40b5e1ce0aefa0598c3682c2a","tid":1155313,"uid":164770,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"還有不少網友更直言，取這2個名字是在侮辱狗，「作為一個有良知的人，我奉勸你一句，你不能用這2個詞侮辱狗狗」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個網民有機會出事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f537813ea17f9ccc848ab89d1e451a086222b9a9","tid":1155313,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f13b0f311f9234f40b5e1ce0aefa0598c3682c2a","tid":1155313,"uid":164770,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"還有不少網友更直言，取這2個名字是在侮辱狗，「作為一個有良知的人，我奉勸你一句，你不能用這2個詞侮辱狗狗」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個網民有機會出事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f38bb038cd76f34fb1f1aa5d24fc7e4c0681f6","tid":1155313,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29399e63c8e5ea03edc4065a139d6a0c3c7b308c","tid":1155313,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:05:55.000Z","msg":"虐畜"},{"pid":"f027d839235f2a61801cc708b0488c7360ff5c95","tid":1155313,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f13b0f311f9234f40b5e1ce0aefa0598c3682c2a","tid":1155313,"uid":164770,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"還有不少網友更直言，取這2個名字是在侮辱狗，「作為一個有良知的人，我奉勸你一句，你不能用這2個詞侮辱狗狗」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個網民有機會出事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:07:27.000Z","msg":"應該係外國先咁夠薑"},{"pid":"8b3b9cb64fe34167ce7ccb2863ee2ff9a5456bea","tid":1155313,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:07:58.000Z","msg":"共狗"},{"pid":"8c98cd421eb662848073a2739ff0df14bda7a2f1","tid":1155313,"uid":41389,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"咁我改我隻狗叫黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4b749e0efd657f71fa4cdaba2f68a06983e27a","tid":1155313,"uid":18685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:09:29.000Z","msg":"文字獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43455386d370c8cab33babd058a63d4c30d76449","tid":1155313,"uid":224510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:12:17.000Z","msg":"不如狗仔實名制<br />\n有埋敏感字filter<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ece22a4c7810d2be3f1bd37a6d96652010d37b","tid":1155313,"uid":207254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:17:49.000Z","msg":"明顯係顛覆國家政權要打靶"},{"pid":"a4da5aa59f44c710a4f41819a413b75fb1332b76","tid":1155313,"uid":52595,"like":6,"dislike"